{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Nebula Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #1a2a6c; /* Deep blue background */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #b224ef, #1a2a6c); /* Gradient from purple to blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about {\n            background-color: #162254; /* Slightly darker blue */\n        }\n        #games {\n            background-color: #1a2a6c;\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #162254;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #b224ef; /* Accent color */\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #1f3a93; /* Lighter blue */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin: 20px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 300px;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .game-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: #b224ef; /* Accent color */\n        }\n        .game-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        input[type=\"text\"],\n        input[type=\"email\"],\n        textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #b224ef; /* Accent color border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #1f3a93; /* Lighter blue background for inputs */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important for consistent sizing */\n        }\n        textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        button {\n            background-color: #b224ef; /* Accent color button */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: #8c1ab8; /* Darker accent on hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0d1a4a; /* Very dark blue */\n            color: #cccccc;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .navbar {\n            background-color: #1a2a6c;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n        }\n        .navbar a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 14px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .navbar a:hover {\n            background-color: #b224ef; /* Accent color on hover */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Nebula Studios</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Worlds, Igniting Imagination</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#games\">Our Games</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Nebula Studios</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to Nebula Studios, where passion meets pixels. We are a dedicated team of game developers, artists, and storytellers driven by a singular vision: to create unforgettable interactive experiences.</p>\n            <p>Founded in 2020, our mission is to push the boundaries of game design, blending innovative mechanics with compelling narratives. We believe in the power of games to connect people, evoke emotions, and explore new frontiers.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"games\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Game+1+Art\" alt=\"Game 1\">\n                <h3>Cosmic Odyssey</h3>\n                <p>Embark on an epic space adventure across a procedurally generated galaxy. Discover alien worlds, manage your starship, and unravel ancient mysteries.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Game+2+Art\" alt=\"Game 2\">\n                <h3>Shadows of Eldoria</h3>\n                <p>A dark fantasy RPG filled with challenging combat, intricate lore, and meaningful player choices. Forge your legend in a world on the brink of collapse.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Game+3+Art\" alt=\"Game 3\">\n                <h3>Pixel Pioneers</h3>\n                <p>A charming retro-style simulation game where you build and manage your own pixel art town, from humble beginnings to a bustling metropolis.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have a business inquiry, a question, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Nebula Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}